# =============================================================
# STEP 2 — After pip install -r requirements.txt, run:
#
#   python -m nltk.downloader punkt stopwords wordnet averaged_perceptron_tagger
#
# STEP 3 — Install spaCy model (pick ONE based on your spaCy version):
#
#   python -m spacy --version        ← check version first
#
#   spaCy 3.7.x:
#   python -m spacy download en_core_web_sm
#   OR direct:
#   pip install https://github.com/explosion/spacy-models/releases/download/en_core_web_sm-3.7.1/en_core_web_sm-3.7.1-py3-none-any.whl
#
#   spaCy 3.6.x:
#   pip install https://github.com/explosion/spacy-models/releases/download/en_core_web_sm-3.6.0/en_core_web_sm-3.6.0-py3-none-any.whl
#
#   spaCy 3.5.x:
#   pip install https://github.com/explosion/spacy-models/releases/download/en_core_web_sm-3.5.0/en_core_web_sm-3.5.0-py3-none-any.whl
#
# IMPORTANT: The portal works WITHOUT spaCy — it falls back to NLTK-only.
# =============================================================
